title: Huron County recognizes top 50 students of 2023
body_text:
The Huron Daily Tribune announced its top-50 students of 2023 during a special ceremony held for the students and their families at the Franklin Inn May 10.
Each year, the top-50 students are determined by a formula that includes their GPA and ACT/SAT scores. Check out all 50 students' bios below.
